ey |url= https://www.masslive.com/politics/2020/01/congressman-joe-kennedy-backed-by-four-lawrence-city-councilors-in-primary-against-sen-ed-markey.html |date=January 31, 2020|publisher=MassLive.com}}</ref>\n\n;Labor unions\n* [[American Federation of Musicians]] Local 9-535<ref>{{cite web |last1=Assn |first1=Boston Musicians |title=Boston Musicians' Association, AFM Local 9-535 endorses Joe Kennedy for Senate. This is music to our ears! @The_AFM @AFLCIO @RepJoeKennedy #JoeKennedy |url=https://twitter.com/BostonMusicians/status/1175413140730851333 |website=@BostonMusicians |publisher=Twitter |language=en |date=September 21, 2019}}</ref>\n*[[International Brotherhood of Electrical Workers]] Local 103<ref name=\"KennedyGlobe\">{{Cite news |url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/metro/2019/09/19/kennedy-expected-entrance-into-senate-race-draws-mixed-reaction-from-fellow-democrats/kCHHN6zVXx1Ssq5ZbhyEBK/story.html |title=Democrats are all over the place on Joe Kennedy\u2019s Senate run |last=McGrane |first=Victoria |date=September 19, 2019 |work=[[The Boston Globe]] |access-date=September 20, 2019 |last2=Krantz |first2=Laura}}</ref>\n* [[International Brotherhood of Teamsters]] Local 25<ref>{{cite web |last1=O'Brien |first1=Sean |title=Teamsters Local 25 Endorse Congressman Joseph P. Kennedy III for U.S. Senate |url=https://scontent-iad3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/71705761_2463231473764813_204007136924008448_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&_nc_oc=AQmB8zLpaguUb-FLf2RpF9EeedqE5mxqXe2SWwkncMP_Rpyb7jO_5kSBynWXJITcHQIUAQle_uoMwWVESPo2QH3C&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.xx&oh=093a3fcaceb217d9adb81763793455d4&oe=5DF22BEC |website=Facebook |date=September 21, 2019}}</ref>\n* Massachusetts State Council of [[International Association of Machinists and Aerospace Workers|Machinists]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Mastandrea |first1=James |last2=Vartabedian |first2=E. Michael |last3=Wells |first3=James |last4=Dunlevy |first4=Keisha |title=Massachusetts State Council of Machinists Endorse Congressman Joe Kennedy III for S