abedian |first2=E. Michael |last3=Wells |first3=James |last4=Dunlevy |first4=Keisha |title=Massachusetts State Council of Machinists Endorse Congressman Joe Kennedy III for Senate {{!}} Machinists Union Local 264 Boston |url=http://iam264boston.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/D4DDF1A3-B740-444A-A1D1-AE56610A3BBE-576x1024.png |date=September 21, 2019}}</ref>\n}}\n\n=== Polling ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%;text-align:center;\"\n|- valign=bottom\n! Poll source\n! Date(s)<br>administered\n! Sample<br>size{{efn|Key:<br>A \u2013 all adults<br>RV \u2013 registered voters<br>LV \u2013 likely voters<br>V \u2013 unclear}}\n! Margin<br>of error\n! style=\"width:65px;\"| Ed<br>Markey\n! style=\"width:65px;\"| Maura<br>Healey\n! style=\"width:65px;\"| Shannon<br>{{nowrap|Liss-Riordan}}\n! style=\"width:65px;\"| Joe<br>{{nowrap|Kennedy III}}\n! style=\"width:65px;\"| Seth<br>Moulton\n! style=\"width:65px;\"| Steve<br>Pemberton\n! style=\"width:65px;\"| Allen <br>Waters\n! style=\"width:65px;\"| Other\n! Undecided\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [https://www.bostonglobe.com/2020/03/01/nation/read-full-results-mass-senate-primary-poll/ Suffolk University/Boston Globe/WBZ][https://assets.documentcloud.org/documents/6791271/FINAL-MA-Marginals-2.pdf]\n|February 26\u201328, 2020\n|465 (LV)\n|\u00b1&nbsp;4.4%\n|36%\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n| {{party shading/Democratic}}|'''42%'''\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|1%{{efn|\"Refused\" with 1%}}\n|21%\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [https://www.wcvb.com/article/umass-amherstwcvb-poll-markey-kennedy-neck-and-neck-for-us-senate-democratic-primary/31144612 UMass Amherst/WCVB][https://htv-prod-media.s3.amazonaws.com/files/supertuesdaymatoplines-1582851435.pdf]\n|February 18\u201324, 2020\n|400 (LV)\n|\u00b1&nbsp;5.9%\n| {{party shading/Democratic}}|'''43%'''\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|40%\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|4%\n|13%\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [https://www.uml.edu/docs/2020-Mass-topline_tcm18-322473.pdf UMass Lowell/Y